HEADWORD: Kenning
<hw>Ken"ning</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See <er>Ken</er>,
<pos>v. t.</pos>]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Range of sight.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Bacon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The limit of vision at sea, being a distance of
about twenty miles.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Keno</ent>⟦br⟧
